{
  "scene_id": "scene_33_marens_trial_the_restricted_stacks",
  "entries": [
    {
      "id": "scene_33_marens_trial_the_restricted_stacks_001",
      "speaker": "younger_maren",
      "lines": [
        "Why did you spend your life on this? Decades\nof study. Exile. Isolation. For what? Knowledge that only brought\nsuffering?"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_33_marens_trial_the_restricted_stacks_002",
      "speaker": "maren",
      "lines": [
        "Knowledge that might end it."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_33_marens_trial_the_restricted_stacks_003",
      "speaker": "younger_maren",
      "lines": [
        "Might. After all those years, the best you\nhave is \"might.\""
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_33_marens_trial_the_restricted_stacks_004",
      "speaker": "maren",
      "lines": [
        "I didn't waste those years. I spent them learning\nhow to do this."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_33_marens_trial_the_restricted_stacks_005",
      "speaker": "sable",
      "lines": [
        "Maren?"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_33_marens_trial_the_restricted_stacks_006",
      "speaker": "maren",
      "lines": [
        "My younger self. Twenty years younger. Sharp.\nCertain. She asked me why I'd wasted my life."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_33_marens_trial_the_restricted_stacks_007",
      "speaker": "edren",
      "lines": [
        "What did you tell her?"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_33_marens_trial_the_restricted_stacks_008",
      "speaker": "maren",
      "lines": [
        "That I spent those years learning how to see the\ntruth. And that seeing the truth is the only weapon that matters\nagainst something that thrives on denial."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_33_marens_trial_the_restricted_stacks_009",
      "speaker": "maren",
      "lines": [
        "I can see the Pallor now. In everything. The way it\nmoves, what it's afraid of. What it feeds on. I understand it."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_33_marens_trial_the_restricted_stacks_010",
      "speaker": "torren",
      "lines": [
        "Is that a good thing?"
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_33_marens_trial_the_restricted_stacks_011",
      "speaker": "maren",
      "lines": [
        "Ask me when this is over."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_33_marens_trial_the_restricted_stacks_012",
      "speaker": "edren",
      "lines": [
        "We all made it through."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_33_marens_trial_the_restricted_stacks_013",
      "speaker": "sable",
      "lines": [
        "Barely."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_33_marens_trial_the_restricted_stacks_014",
      "speaker": "lira",
      "lines": [
        "No. Not barely. The Pallor tested us at our weakest\npoints, and our weakest points turned out to be load-bearing."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_33_marens_trial_the_restricted_stacks_015",
      "speaker": "maren",
      "lines": [
        "The lesson. Each trial: the Pallor feeds on denial.\nAcceptance starves it. That's why we're still standing."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    },
    {
      "id": "scene_33_marens_trial_the_restricted_stacks_016",
      "speaker": "torren",
      "lines": [
        "Then let's not waste what we learned."
      ],
      "condition": null,
      "animations": null,
      "choice": null,
      "sfx": null
    }
  ]
}
